DiscoveryType DiscoveryType Enum

In this Article

Edit

Describes the publishing behavior of a service in the Service Registry.

Syntax

Declaration

[DataContract(Name = "DiscoveryType", Namespace = "http://schemas.microsoft.com/netservices/2009/05/servicebus/connect")]
public enum DiscoveryType<DataContract(Name:="DiscoveryType", Namespace:="http://schemas.microsoft.com/netservices/2009/05/servicebus/connect")>
Public Enum DiscoveryType

Fields

Private
Private

The service will not be published in the Service Registry.
Public
Public

The Service will be published in the Service Registry.

Attributes

System.Runtime.Serialization.DataContractAttribute

Details

Namespace

Microsoft.ServiceBus

Assembly

Microsoft.ServiceBus.dll
